<h1>Images</h1>

<h3><%= step %></h3>
<p>Save the <a href="client_logo.png">Flatchat logo</a> to 'flatchat/logo.png'</p>

<h3><%= step %></h3>
<p>Change <code>&lt;h1&gt;Flatchat&lt;/h1&gt;</code> to:</p>
<pre>
&lt;h1&gt;
  &lt;img src="logo.png" height="24"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;
  &lt;span&gt;Flatchat&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
</pre>
<p>Reload the page.</p>

<h3><%= step %></h3>
<p>Add to <code>&lt;head&gt;</code>:</p>
<pre>
&lt;link rel="shortcut icon" href="logo.png"&gt;
</pre>
<p>Reload the page. To get the browser to load the icon you will need to open file and reopen tab.</p>
